{"tid":2390610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"進擊的韭菜！中國騎士遭攔下 爆氣狂毆交通警察","createTime":"2021-02-01T15:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T06:12:27.000Z","uid":337052,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"558765628fc566f78ccea5237e2a47e836f967c7","tid":2390610,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">進擊的韭菜！中國騎士遭攔下 爆氣狂毆交通警察</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/02/01/phpVN3IMJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F02%2F01%2FphpVN3IMJ.jpg&h=3d5d09f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國員警半路攔查騎士開罰，被對方痛毆。（圖取自微博）<br />\n<br />\n2021/02/01 22:47<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國警方強力執法，每年開出的罰單總金額將近人民幣3000億元，折合台幣約1兆2995億元，<span class=\"red\">廣州1名機車騎士不滿被交通警察半路攔下，竟爆氣失控把交警打到一度站不起來，但他最後也因此吃上官司，網友對此直呼「進擊的韭菜」。</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合中國媒體報導，2021年1月29日，中國廣東省廣州市1名男子，騎著摩托車在當地中山六路上，因交通違法被交警攔下勸阻，<span class=\"red\">男子對此突然爆氣，對著交通警察一陣拳打腳踢，不等交警有所反應，騎士更摘下安全帽狠狠毆打，旁邊民眾全程錄影，無人勸阻。</span><br />\n<br />\n該名交通警察一度被打到躺在地上、爬不起來，不過最後還是站起身子對騎士開罰，動粗的男子事後怒氣消除，卻也已經涉嫌妨害公務罪，被當地警方依照中國法律施以刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，中國政府每年對人民開出的罰單總金額接近人民幣3000億元，可能因此導致民怨，許多網友看完影片，紛紛留言指出「真戰狼，每次都是打自己人最狠」、「你有壓力，我也有壓力」、「習近平新時代中國特色社會主義應對執法人員的行為」、「中國安全帽竟然沒被砸爛」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=420904255842653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D420904255842653&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=0c2e3e46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=420904255842653</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3429117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3429117&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=097cb8b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3429117&h=08e58fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3429117</a>"},{"pid":"9b83262a0bac54df86ce858c8d79d8888ec07c22","tid":2390610,"uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:56:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IIdYQqDRK1U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIIdYQqDRK1U&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=f9f5effa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IIdYQqDRK1U</a><br />\n速遞員失控狂毆交警"},{"pid":"457f8219af3cd06cfa9c84dbb5671a9f1074302f","tid":2390610,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:56:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RFA_Chinese/status/1356163306122137602?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRFA_Chinese%2Fstatus%2F1356163306122137602%3Fs%3D20&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=abcd1ccd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRFA_Chinese%2Fstatus%2F1356163306122137602%3Fs%3D20&h=23a087ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RFA_Chinese/status/1356163306122137602?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"4d54ebc2e94c9746e86733e5cdbffb503b425ab6","tid":2390610,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"牛b"},{"pid":"ba2116a3117058e73b1bfa908b6a847a3fe47e4d","tid":2390610,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:01:14.000Z","msg":"學黑警咁，第一下又或者挨多兩下瞓底咪冇咁傷囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c50276a502b916cbc4517d6eaaadde9cd0d279e","tid":2390610,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8dd1020861404cd0ee4a7b381844d07c1cbc62","tid":2390610,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q